  "title": "惠灵顿之旅 Wellington",
  "summary": "公路旅行，往返奥克兰惠灵顿，6天5晚。 惠灵顿知名的缆车，惠灵顿的地势没有奥克兰那么平坦，这个缆车帮助了很多人 […]",
  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-18.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>公路旅行，往返奥克兰惠灵顿，6天5晚。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-17.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>惠灵顿知名的缆车，惠灵顿的地势没有奥克兰那么平坦，这个缆车帮助了很多人通勤。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-15.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>惠灵顿的城区高楼大厦很多，比奥克兰看起来更繁华。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-19.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>坐落在繁华角落的二手书店。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-20.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>惠灵顿火车站。其实并没有很多火车。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-21.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>惠灵顿机场。其实并没有奥克兰机场那么繁忙。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-12.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>接下来都是路上的见闻了，蓝泉的水依然很清澈。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-13.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>我想吟诗一首：</p>\n\n\n\n<p>轻轻的我走了，<br>正如我轻轻的来；<br>我轻轻的招手，<br>作别西天的云彩。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>那河畔的金柳，<br>是夕阳中的新娘；<br>波光里的艳影，<br>在我的心头荡漾。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>软泥上的青荇，<br>油油的在水底招摇；<br>在康河的柔波里，<br>我甘心做一条水草！</p>\n\n\n\n<p>那榆荫下的一潭，<br>不是清泉，是天上虹；<br>揉碎在浮藻间，<br>沉淀着彩虹似的梦。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>寻梦？撑一支长篙，<br>向青草更青处漫溯；<br>满载一船星辉，<br>在星辉斑斓里放歌。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>但我不能放歌，<br>悄悄是别离的笙箫；<br>夏虫也为我沉默，<br>沉默是今晚的康桥！</p>\n\n\n\n<p>悄悄的我走了，<br>正如我悄悄的来；<br>我挥一挥衣袖，<br>不带走一片云彩。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-14.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>鸟瞰Whanganui。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-16.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>接下来都是水了。这张是Rotorua的水。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-11.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>接下来都是Napier的水。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-22.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Napier的水我觉得是新西兰水的天花板。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-23.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>白浪花，黑沙滩。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-25.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>沙滩又长又平坦。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-26.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>人也不多，想怎么拍都可以。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/image-24.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>天气好的时候有一抹绿色。</p>",
